WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
As Ziggy, Bowie often wore an earring in just one ear. 

00:04.500 --> 00:09.500
He had a range of various ornate designs, including a simple hoop earring 

00:10.000 --> 00:14.000
for the last throes of the Ziggy look in the 'Rebel Rebel' video. 

00:15.000 --> 00:19.500
This particular leopard-print accessory is believed to have been given to him 

00:20.000 --> 00:23.500
by the actress in the video for The Jean Genie, Cyrinda Foxe.